<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Painel da Semana — A Voz da Foto</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { background: #2A2A2A; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }

  .canvas {
    width: 1080px;
    height: 1920px;
    background: #F5EFE6;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 80px 70px 70px;
    color: #282D29;
  }

  /* textura sutil */
  .canvas::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(185,76,20,.04) 0, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(198,134,67,.05) 0, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* cantos viewfinder */
  .viewfinder { position: absolute; width: 36px; height: 36px; border: 2.5px solid #B94C14; }
  .vf-tl { top: 36px; left: 36px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .vf-tr { top: 36px; right: 36px; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; }
  .vf-bl { bottom: 36px; left: 36px; border-right: none; border-top: none; }
  .vf-br { bottom: 36px; right: 36px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

  /* header */
  .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 32px; position: relative; z-index: 2;}
  .brand { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; font-size: 24px; color: #B94C14; letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .week { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; color: #282D29; opacity: .55; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  h1 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 92px; line-height: .92; letter-spacing: -2px; color: #282D29; margin-bottom: 6px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #B94C14; font-weight: 500;}
  .sub { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 400; color: #282D29; opacity: .65; margin-bottom: 38px; max-width: 720px; line-height: 1.45; position: relative; z-index: 2; }

  /* divisor */
  .div { height: 1px; background: #282D29; opacity: .14; margin: 0 0 28px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }

  /* zona vermelha */
  .red-zone { background: #B94C14; color: #F5EFE6; padding: 28px 32px; border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 36px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .red-zone .red-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: .3px;}
  .red-zone ol { list-style: none; counter-reset: r; }
  .red-zone li { counter-increment: r; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.45; padding: 9px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(245,239,230,.25); display: flex; gap: 14px; }
  .red-zone li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .red-zone li::before { content: counter(r); font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; min-width: 26px; opacity: .85;}
  .red-zone li strong { font-weight: 600; }
  .red-zone .who { font-size: 13px; opacity: .75; font-style: italic; margin-left: 6px;}

  /* colunas */
  .cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .col { background: #FEFEFE; border: 1px solid rgba(40,45,41,.10); padding: 24px 22px; border-radius: 2px; }
  .col-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 600; color: #B94C14; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .col-role { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: #282D29; opacity: .55; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;}
  .col ul { list-style: none; }
  .col li { font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.42; padding: 11px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(40,45,41,.08); color: #282D29; display: flex; gap: 8px;}
  .col li:last-child { border-bottom: none;}
  .col li .id { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 600; color: #C68643; min-width: 24px; font-size: 16px;}
  .col li .when { font-size: 11.5px; color: #B94C14; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; margin-top: 2px; display: block;}

  /* footer */
  .footer { position: absolute; bottom: 88px; left: 70px; right: 70px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; z-index: 2;}
  .ritual { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #282D29; opacity: .65;}
  .ritual strong { font-weight: 600; color: #B94C14; opacity: 1;}
  .stamp { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 19px; color: #282D29; opacity: .55;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="canvas">
    <div class="viewfinder vf-tl"></div>
    <div class="viewfinder vf-tr"></div>
    <div class="viewfinder vf-bl"></div>
    <div class="viewfinder vf-br"></div>

    <div class="header">
      <span class="brand">A Voz da Foto</span>
      <span class="week">Sprint · 18 a 22 maio</span>
    </div>

    <h1>Painel da<br><em>semana</em></h1>
    <p class="sub">Cinco dias pra destravar. Cada tarefa tem dono único, prazo e o que destrava a próxima. Ana e Isa, leiam de cima pra baixo.</p>

    <div class="div"></div>

    <div class="red-zone">
      <div class="red-title">Zona vermelha · destravar hoje</div>
      <ol>
        <li><div><strong>Preço final do Café com Foto</strong> — R$ 53 ou R$ 97?<span class="who"> · Ana decide</span></div></li>
        <li><div><strong>Número de WhatsApp oficial</strong> pra LP e CTAs<span class="who"> · Ana confirma</span></div></li>
        <li><div><strong>Data + local do 1º Café</strong> em Brasília<span class="who"> · Ana define</span></div></li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="cols">
      <!-- LEANDRO -->
      <div class="col">
        <div class="col-name">Leandro</div>
        <div class="col-role">Execução técnica</div>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="id">L1</span><div>Trocar WhatsApp na LP <span class="when">Seg, após Ana</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">L2</span><div>Subir vídeos no GDrive da Voz <span class="when">Seg à noite</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">L3</span><div>Publicar 3 reels (1 por dia) <span class="when">Ter–Qui</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">L4</span><div>Exportar C16, C17, C18 <span class="when">Qua</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">L5</span><div>og:image novo na LP <span class="when">Quando I1 sair</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">L6</span><div>Aquecer Meta 15min/dia <span class="when">Toda semana</span></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- ANA -->
      <div class="col">
        <div class="col-name">Ana</div>
        <div class="col-role">Decisões + operação</div>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="id">A1</span><div>Decidir preço do Café <span class="when">Segunda</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">A2</span><div>WhatsApp oficial <span class="when">Segunda</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">A3</span><div>Copy dos 3 reels (4 linhas + tags) <span class="when">Terça</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">A4</span><div>Data + local do 1º Café <span class="when">Quarta</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">A5</span><div>Aprovar legendas C16–C18 <span class="when">Quarta</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">A6</span><div>20 perfis-referência pra Isa <span class="when">Sexta</span></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- ISA -->
      <div class="col">
        <div class="col-name">Isa</div>
        <div class="col-role">Rosto + estética</div>
        <ul>
          <li><span class="id">I1</span><div>Marcar ensaio autoral próprio <span class="when">Terça</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">I2</span><div>Gravar 3 reels novos (1/dia) <span class="when">Qua–Sex</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">I3</span><div>Aprovar estética C16–C18 <span class="when">Quarta</span></div></li>
          <li><span class="id">I4</span><div>Aprovar foto pro og:image <span class="when">Quinta</span></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="ritual">
        <strong>Ritual:</strong> Segunda 9h painel · Quarta 18h check · Sexta 17h fechamento
      </div>
      <div class="stamp">— ler é decidir.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
